The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to remove shadows from photographs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves image synthesis and graphics, which could fall under cs.GR (Computer Graphics). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to refine the results, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves artificial intelligence techniques, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves statistical learning techniques to evaluate the results, which could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
